criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Above 18 years of age;

          2. Belonging to the transplant queue of InCor;

          3. Eligible for sequential bilateral lung transplantation submitted to clamshell
             incision;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients undergoing a new surgical procedure after lung transplantation with the need
             to manipulate the steel wires or the sternal fixation plate other than for
             osteomyelitis;

          2. Intraoperative death;

          3. Patients who have undergone unilateral lung transplantation or have not undergone a
             clamshell incision.
